spec_data.Name: avr-binutils
spec_data.Description:
This is a Cross Compiling version of GNU binutils, which can be used to
assemble and link binaries for the avr platform, instead of for the
native x86_64 platform.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Mon 07 Aug 2017 03:47:41 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Cross Compiling GNU binutils targeted at avr
